OL,3,CRare Guernsey goat breed set to
OL,4,Creceive Royal title
OL,6,FGuernsey's Golden goats will be
OL,7,Fgranted a Royal title when the King
OL,8,Fand Queen visit the island on Tuesday
OL,9,F(16 July).
OL,11,FIt will be the first time in recent
OL,12,Fhistory that the honour has been given
OL,13,Fto a livestock breed.
OL,15,FIt will apply to all Golden Guernseys
OL,16,Facross the world, and they will
OL,17,Fformally be known as the Royal Golden
OL,18,FGuernsey Goat.
