OL,3,CRare Guernsey goat breed set to
OL,4,Creceive Royal title
OL,6,FTheir Majesties will officially bestow
OL,7,Fthe title by placing an engraved brass
OL,8,Fbell on a collar around the neck of an
OL,9,Feight-year-old female Golden Guernsey
OL,10,Fcalled Summerville Tamsin.
OL,12,FThe dairy goats are a rare breed which
OL,13,Fhave been native to the island for at
OL,14,Fleast 200 years.
OL,16,FThey are characterised by their golden
OL,17,Fcoloured skin and hair and their
OL,18,Ffriendly behaviour.
