OL,3,CRare Guernsey goat breed set to
OL,4,Creceive Royal title
OL,6,FGuernsey's Lieutenant-Governor Richard
OL,7,FCripwell said: "The recognition being
OL,8,Fgranted to our special and rare breed,
OL,9,Fthe Golden Guernsey, is a wonderful
OL,10,Fand fitting way to mark the
OL,11,Fsignificance of His Majesty's first
OL,12,Fvisit to the island as King, an island
OL,13,Fwhose relationship with the Crown is
OL,14,Fat its core constitutionally as well
OL,15,Fas historically.
OL,17,F"It's a legacy and a tremendous honour
OL,18,Fthat will stay with Guernsey for
OL,19,Ffuture generations."
