OL,3,CRare Guernsey goat breed set to
OL,4,Creceive Royal title
OL,6,FChristopher Price, Chief Executive of
OL,7,Fthe Rare Breeds Survival Trust - of
OL,8,Fwhich the King is a Patron - said the
OL,9,Ftitle reflects the Golden Guernsey's
OL,10,F"cultural and historical significance"
OL,11,Falongside their "value to
OL,12,Fbiodiversity".
OL,14,FHe said: "Golden Guernseys are really
OL,15,Fefficient milk producers, and the milk
OL,16,Fis great for making yoghurt or cheese.
