OL,6,F"The breed also excels in conservation
OL,7,Fgrazing which supports biodiversity.
OL,8,FBeing choosey in what they eat, their
OL,9,Fgrazing can provide very specific
OL,10,Fenvironmental benefits."
OL,12,FHe added: "We are extremely grateful
OL,13,Fto His Majesty for his continued,
OL,14,Fgreatly valued support for British
OL,15,Frare native livestock and equine
OL,16,Fbreeds."
